data.description: Don't miss this beautiful home that has so much to offer!  This home has 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, a personal above ground pool with a privacy fence in the back yard and a nice front porch for sitting and enjoying some down time. Inside, you will find a spacious living room with a fireplace and hardwood floors, large bedrooms and walk in closets, 9+ ft ceilings and more! The property is just minutes from the interstate and is in the Verbena School districts. Book your showing today!
